[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    183[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### Networking Expert Review
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    184[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    185[0m:[38;5;10m[49m #### N1 - HIGH: VPC Endpoint List Is Incomplete
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    186[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    187[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Location:** Prerequisites table, "VPC" row
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    188[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    189[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Issue:** The recipe states "VPC endpoints for S3 and Glue." This is incomplete. The architecture uses Lambda in a VPC connecting to multiple AWS services. Without VPC endpoints, the Lambda functions need a NAT Gateway for internet access, which introduces PHI egress risk and adds cost.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    190[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
