[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    192[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - `com.amazonaws.{region}.kms` (Interface) - Lambda needs KMS for envelope encryption/decryption
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    193[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - `com.amazonaws.{region}.logs` (Interface) - Lambda needs CloudWatch Logs for logging
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    194[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - `com.amazonaws.{region}.monitoring` (Interface) - CloudWatch metrics
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    195[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - `com.amazonaws.{region}.states` (Interface) - Step Functions state reporting
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    196[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - `com.amazonaws.{region}.events` (Interface) - EventBridge for schedule triggers
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    197[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The recipe mentions "VPC endpoints for S3 and Glue" but Glue does not have a VPC endpoint for the Glue API itself (Glue jobs run in their own managed VPC). The correct endpoint is for the Glue Data Catalog if Lambda needs to access it.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
