[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m VPC Endpoints Required:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - com.amazonaws.{region}.s3              (Gateway - for bulk load files, source data)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - com.amazonaws.{region}.dynamodb        (Gateway - if using DynamoDB for query caching)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - com.amazonaws.{region}.neptune-db      (Interface - Neptune query access, if using IAM auth)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - com.amazonaws.{region}.kms             (Interface - envelope encryption)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - com.amazonaws.{region}.logs            (Interface - CloudWatch Logs)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - com.amazonaws.{region}.monitoring      (Interface - CloudWatch Metrics)
