[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - com.amazonaws.{region}.events          (Interface - EventBridge)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Neptune is VPC-native and accessed via its cluster endpoint DNS within the VPC.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m No NAT Gateway should be required for the query path.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
