[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Suggested fix:** Add a brief note: "Deploy Neptune with a read replica in a different AZ for automatic failover. Neptune Multi-AZ failover typically completes in under 30 seconds. The query Lambda should use the Neptune reader endpoint for read queries to automatically route to available replicas."
