[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    325[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 2. **GINA compliance (S2)** - Genetic data has heightened regulatory protection. The recipe must address this architecturally, not just mention it in passing.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    326[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 3. **VPC endpoint completeness (N1)** - Missing endpoints will cause Lambda timeouts in VPC deployment. The current list is incorrect (Glue doesn't have a relevant endpoint for this pattern).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    327[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 4. **Bulk load consistency (A1)** - Clinical queries during graph updates could return partial/incorrect results. Commit to a zero-downtime update strategy.
